{"tid":1080392,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"跨部門觀塘掃黃　拉15內地女","createTime":"2019-03-27T14:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T02:17:18.000Z","uid":60658,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"47e7f3a683430be3f3aa793a9c2219ef1be75418","tid":1080392,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"03月27日(三) 21:02   <br />\n觀塘警區特別職務隊、特遣隊、雜項調查隊及秀茂坪警區特別職務隊聯同入境事務處人員，今日（27日）中午約12時展開代號「孤影」及「萬里達」的掃黃行動，突擊搜查通明街、宜安街、康寧道、崇仁街、輔仁街、<span style=\"color: red;\">瑞和街</span>及觀塘商貿區一帶，共拘捕15名年齡介乎19至48歲的持雙程證內地女子，涉嫌違反逗留條件。所有被捕女子已被扣留調查，稍後交由入境事務處跟進。"},{"pid":"acd17b52695c358ed4de8d67ec61ee4c6fcfeee6","tid":1080392,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"觀塘咁多罪案，放針嗰位(港父)真係冇做錯。"},{"pid":"8526d1c3f9bbad615e4f889745af3292b7a80ea2","tid":1080392,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"acd17b52695c358ed4de8d67ec61ee4c6fcfeee6","tid":1080392,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"觀塘咁多罪案，放針嗰位(港父)真係冇做錯。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e33e8823da0befbb7941509e9f3e4df2e7b2594","tid":1080392,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"acd17b52695c358ed4de8d67ec61ee4c6fcfeee6","tid":1080392,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"觀塘咁多罪案，放針嗰位(港父)真係冇做錯。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"咪屈港父 係樓主放"},{"pid":"f4858c112be19b59a9e2aa4ff086d2b16dc930a3","tid":1080392,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"8e33e8823da0befbb7941509e9f3e4df2e7b2594","tid":1080392,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"acd17b52695c358ed4de8d67ec61ee4c6fcfeee6","tid":1080392,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"觀塘咁多罪案